episodes.title: GETTING INTO ESCAPING TWIN FLAMES
episodes.description: *Spoiler Alert*  What better time of year to binge watch a docuseries, about love, than February?! Escaping Twin Flames is a docuseries on Netflix that follows the journey of people in search of their 'Twin Flame' or destined love. The show breaks down the experiences people have had or are currently living through with the online cult, Twin Flames Universe. Sarah & Katrina discuss this cult following, the two leaders, the concept of a Twin Flame, and the lengths some people went through in the hopes of finding their forever love. Tune in now and share your feedback on LETS GET INTO IT's socials!  Special thank you to this episode's sponsors, Discover and McDonald's!
